 MacOS
*****

Tested on MacOS Tahoe 26.3.1.

Install the latero and latero-graphics libraries.

Build the app
>> cmake -B build
>> cmake --build build

Run the app
>> build/src/latero-demo
 
 Create an app bundle (currently broken)
 >> ../create_app_bundle.sh
You should now be able to launch the program by clicking on the latero-demo app bundle.
